; Transportation
''Bus''
* From {{ill|lt=Ebara Station|Q871691|WD=Q871691|1=Ebara Station}} (JR West San'in Main Line), take Ina-car bus for Kannabe Kōgen, get off at Ishii, about 20 min, then 1 min on foot

''Car''
